<og:type>article</og:type>
<og:description>If you’re not a big fan of the crowded app layout on the Apple Watch, WatchOS 4 has introduced a simpler alternative that makes it easier to scroll through and locate an app.</og:description>
<og:image>https://www.howtogeek.com/thumbcache/648/248/8e54f23d88bcc71f4a9035fcbe96a2b7/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/IMG_3763-copy.jpg</og:image>
