<og:title>How to Set Up Alexa Routines to Control Multiple Smarthome Devices at Once</og:title>
<og:type>article</og:type>
<og:description>It’s great to control your smart house with your voice, but it’s even better when you can say one command and have multiple things happen at once. Here’s how to set up Routines to use with Alexa and your Echo devices.</og:description>
<og:image>https://www.howtogeek.com/thumbcache/648/248/28623021c8fb32e91861ac9742311171/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/IMG_8351.jpg</og:image>
